'''''Anjatha Singam''''' (English: Fearless Lion) is a [[1987 in film|1987]] [[Tamil language|Tamil]]  [[Cinema of India|Indian]] [[feature film]] [[Film director|directed]] by M. Vijaychander for Karthik Arts. The film stars [[Prabhu Ganesan|Prabhu]], [[Sathyaraj]], [[M. N. Nambiar]], [[Nalini (actress)|Nalini]] and [[Goundamani]] in the lead roles.<ref>{{cite web|title=Anjatha Singam LP Vinyl Records|url=http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers/71/3/1/1|publisher=musicalaya|accessdate=2014-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140424235149/http://musicalaya.net/imgviewer.php?mod=lpcovers%2F71%2F3%2F1%2F1|archive-date=24 April 2014|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

